        <p>In 1995 <strong>Joseph J. (JJ) Allaire</strong> co-founded <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Allaire Corporation', 'C'); ?> with his brother <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Jeremy Allaire', 'P'); ?>, creating the web development tool <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('ColdFusion', 'L'); ?>.</p>
        <p>In March 2001, Allaire Corporation was sold to <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Macromedia', 'C'); ?> where ColdFusion was integrated into the <strong>Macromedia MX</strong> product line.</p>
        <p>Macromedia was subsequently acquired by <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Adobe Systems', 'C'); ?>, which continues to develop and market ColdFusion.</p>
